title: Boynton Beach Rentals 1 and 2 Bedrooms
posting_body: ['ATTENTION:', 'PLEASE DO NOT CONTACT ME UNTIL YOU HAVE READ EVERYTHING BELOW.', "Due to the shortness of the Rental Inventory don't delay in seeing them.", 'Please text me with your full name, email address, and phone #, specify a city, # Bedrooms and Pet information, maximum Rent budget, gross monthly income must be at least 3 times the rent amount also what you think your credit scores are.', 'Pets that may have size, weight, and breed restrictions.', 'Also please be advised that rentals require 3 times the Rent Amount plus application fees to move in.', 'Please be advised that some may be already Rented by the time you contact me.', 'Also, some may require a high credit score.', 'Credit score less than 600 need not contact me.', 'It is believed that the information is accurate.', 'Pool is for illustration only.', 'All are Unfurnished and not in  over 55 Community', 'No Section 8  or problems with Background Check', "TEXT 'Bill' at", 'show contact info', 'Without the information requested above I will not be able to assist you!!!!!!!!!!!', 'To begin the process only TEXT me with the information below.', 'Boynton Beach Rentals', 'Unfurnished', '1 Bedroom $1800 to $1800  No Pets', '1 Bedroom $1600 to $1600 Pets', '2 Bedroom $2250 to $2500 No Pets', '2 Bedroom $1950 to $2500 Pets']
